{"type":"message","id":"eaf46b81","parentId":"2d2a2347","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:31:38.759Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nGood, I can see there are historical review reports. Let me read the most recent report to understand the context and then perform today's analysis. Since there are no trades executed today (no positions, no trades), this is a special case where I need to analyze the planned vs actual but no actual trades occurred.\n\nLet me read the latest report first to understand the format, then proceed with the analysis.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f7ccf0352a441e997b65f17","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/strategies/reports/post_market_review_20260401.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":194,"output":122,"cacheRead":51854,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52170,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775125882446}}
{"type":"message","id":"db1145e7","parentId":"eaf46b81","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:31:38.768Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8f7ccf0352a441e997b65f17","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 盘后复盘报告 - 2026-04-01\n\n## 📊 今日总览\n\n### 交易系统状态\n- **系统状态**: ERROR（第4天）\n- **异常原因**: xtdata 模块导入失败 (since 2026-03-28)\n- **计划持仓**: 3只（未执行）\n- **实际成交**: 0笔\n\n### 资金状况\n- **可用资金**: 10,000,000.00 元\n- **总资产**: 10,000,000.00 元\n\n### 假设情景（若按计划执行）\n- **假设收益**: -74.7 元 (-0.07%)\n- **中利集团**: -8.30% 触发止损 → 止损纪律生效\n- **津药药业**: +9.92% 接近涨停 → 盈利\n- **杭电股份**: -0.39% 正常波动\n\n## 📈 个股表现明细\n\n| 股票 | 代码 | 行业 | 仓位 | 止损/止盈 | 今日涨跌 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|------|-----------|----------|------|\n| 中利集团 | 002309 | 电力设备 | 5.8% | -8%/+15% | -8.30% | 🛑触发止损 |\n| 津药药业 | 600488 | 医药生物 | 4.3% | -6%/+12% | +9.92% | 🔥接近止盈 |\n| 杭电股份 | 603618 | 电力设备 | 5.6% | -8%/+15% | -0.39% | 正常波动 |\n\n### 新闻分析\n- **中利集团 -8.30%**: 3/23异动公告+3/6限售解禁7941万股，前期炒作资金获利了结\n- **津药药业 +9.92%**: 创新药概念活跃，个股逆行业downtrend大涨\n- **杭电股份 -0.39%**: 3/27涨停后缩量回调，年内涨幅已超170%\n\n## 🔬 因子有效性排行榜\n\n### 最有效 TOP3\n1. 机构资金流向 - 命中率100.0%\n2. 行业动量 - 命中率100.0%\n3. 换手率异动 - 命中率100.0%\n\n### 最失效 TOP3\n1. PE/PB低估值 - 命中率0.0%\n2. ML模型预测 - 命中率0.0%\n3. 市场状态 - 命中率0.0%\n\n## 🎓 教训总结\n1. **系统可靠性是第一风控** - 连续4天异常必须建立降级方案\n2. **异动公告=风险信号** - 中利3/23异动后今日暴跌\n3. **限售解禁=减分因子** - 需新增到因子库\n4. **行业regime≠个股regime** - 个股因子权重应高于行业\n\n## 🎯 明日关注\n1. 🔧 修复xtdata模块（紧急）\n2. 新增异动公告+限售解禁过滤器\n3. 中东局势→能源/黄金板块\n4. 亚太反弹4.3%→A股跟涨持续性\n\n---\n*报告生成时间: 2026-04-01 18:30 CST*\n*分析师: 柴荣 (Chai Rong)*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775125898765}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e1630ff","parentId":"db1145e7","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:31:45.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nNow I understand the context. The system has been in ERROR state for several days due to xtdata module issues. Today (2026-04-02) shows no trades were executed at all, indicating the system is either completely down or there were no signals generated.\n\nSince there are no positions and no trades, I need to:\n1. Update the factor tracking file with today's data (though there are no new signals)\n2. Generate a report for today noting the system status\n3. Check for any news analysis (but since there are no positions >5%, no news needed)\n4. Create the markdown report\n5. Send the email\n\nLet me first update the factor tracking file with today's data, then proceed with the report generation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_13e5f46c00984623b617f7b4","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace-chairong/strategies/reports/factor_tracking.json","oldText":"{\n  \"description\": \"因子有效性追踪数据，每日盘后复盘自动更新\",\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-04-01T18:33:44.838079\",\n  \"trading_days\": [],","newText":"{\n  \"description\": \"因子有效性追踪数据，每日盘后复盘自动更新\",\n  \"last_updated\": \"2026-04-02T18:30:00.000000\",\n  \"trading_days\": [\"20260402\"],"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":786,"output":305,"cacheRead":52169,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53260,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775125898768}}
